## Lab Milestones

- Using a simulator (Gazebo)
- Connecting simulator to ROS 2
- Navigation ROS messages (pose, odometry, sensor messages, TF)
- World frame vs robot frames
- Controlling a physical robot with ROS 2
- Integrating sensors with physical robot using ROS
- Live readings to RViz from a physical robot
- Using SLAM Toolbox
- Using Nav2 for full stack development:
  - Navigation
  - Motion planning
  - Obstacle avoidance
  - Going on missions, etc.
